{"tid":1470852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（前線麻煩入一入）可唔可以忍下手？","createTime":"2019-08-14T06:51:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T11:53:08.000Z","uid":98542,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e9171143e1926ecda97822c93f2b9991fa7b24cd","tid":1470852,"uid":98542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:51:44.000Z","msg":"和理飛做文宣<br />\n有時真係需要前線配合<br />\n即係戰場上都要有時退兩步<br />\n等時機成熟再攻上三步<br />\n（我已經當大家係戰友，唔好介意）<br />\n我明白撤退對前線嚟講<br />\n咁樣同侮辱前人功勞冇分別<br />\n但係退一步海闊天空<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">文宣既工作就係需要時間<br />\n用媒體煲大前線發生既事</span><br />\n但近呢半個月<br />\n戰線闊咗，發生既野亦都多咗<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">其實好多非勇武，甚至藍絲既<br />\n都表示話可唔可以叫勇武停一停<br />\n俾啲時間佢哋消化下</span><br />\n同樣既問題亦都發生係外國媒體<br />\n好多報道都係跟唔切香港現況<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唯有用「chaotic」(混亂) 呢啲字眼去形容前線</span><br />\n咁樣亦都令到外國人見到都開始卻步<br />\n因為佢哋冇香港人咁叻<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">佢哋處理唔到咁多資訊<br />\n甚至冇「fact check」既概念</span><br />\n所以先會有尋日同旅客既衝突<br />\n咁樣其實只係令前線企係劣勢入面<br />\n無論打咩仗都好<br />\n企係「高地」永遠都係易打好多<br />\n文宣都係一樣<br />\n係虛偽咗啲，但我哋正正需要外國人支持<br />\n甚至我相信不久既將來<br />\n佢哋都會加入對抗中國共產黨既戰線<br />\n<br />\n我自己都有做過工兵<br />\n睇到前線效率我都真係五體投地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但都希望各位作為前線勇武既<br />\n俾啲時間、空間俾和理飛做野<br />\n亦都當係作前線調整<br />\n大家或者可以諗下點樣「撤得有霸氣」<br />\n同埋<span style=\"color: red;\">打啲值得我地打落手既野</span>（e.g. 林奠）<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兄弟爬山，各有各做</span>"},{"pid":"3f979445f1abdafdabe5874c3b7b9add71dd76b4","tid":1470852,"uid":283179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:54:14.000Z","msg":"冷處理 聚焦818"},{"pid":"cb6a5e9ad1636eb397dac921d4c240b99bd5e389","tid":1470852,"uid":98542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:59:23.000Z","msg":"我只係唔想搞到好亂<br />\n我指既係訊息既混亂<br />\n前線太努力，和理非都會好辛苦<br />\n話晒都係冷氣軍師<br />\n唔係個個都可以日日好似上前線咁頭腦清晰架"},{"pid":"9a431c24bdc51200c8f1d22efd57b5c303ce95a6","tid":1470852,"uid":98542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:42:17.000Z","msg":"屌，冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff46c00c993df2865b8c2d4606cb0e2e63cb4121","tid":1470852,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:42:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg&h=42f5c084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png&h=4a3dc024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg&h=42d70b2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2524008327c3adc69416178c88e46b0cea961d13","tid":1470852,"uid":304894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:45:08.000Z","msg":"我撐你嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eebaef377bf60e87f993bb73b2729bddedbcac0","tid":1470852,"uid":263708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:47:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">「重要！同我勁推」有高人教路如何找出popo前線鬼的痕跡<br />\n<br />\n睇下佢身份證簽發日期,因為popo係優先換證的。日期係由2018年12月27日至2019年3月30日。如係呢三個月,就九成九了。<br />\n如果隻鬼係打算長期混入去D團體度的,便例外。<br />\n如條友唔比身份證你睇,即係唔交心,更要小心<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都是聽番來 不確定有冇用 希望幫到巴絲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">我P牌開唔到新post今日 唔介意有巴絲copy開個專門post緊急宣傳比大家知道同研究</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"ceaa044d8a295a83eebc3dc63185e7415a9ac9de","tid":1470852,"uid":132287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:49:47.000Z","msg":"幫你推下"},{"pid":"190d50349045720801b36a218b5c063e036a8cb4","tid":1470852,"uid":98542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2524008327c3adc69416178c88e46b0cea961d13","tid":1470852,"uid":304894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:45:08.000Z","msg":"我撐你嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:53:08.000Z","msg":"冇野<br />\n純粹係因為都用咗好多時間打呢篇野<br />\n覺得唔抵啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但自己又on9唔想自推<br />\n由得佢自己沉啦"}]}